company_name: HEINRICH SEIFFERT & SOHN GMBH PFEIFEN- UND TABAK - IMPORT
information: The company HEINRICH SEIFFERT & SOHN GMBH PFEIFEN- UND TABAK - IMPORT, is a Wholesaler, founded in 1949, which operates in the Tobacco and smokers items industry. It also operates in the Tobacco industries. It is based in Kassel, Germany.
